      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長瀬麻奈トリビュートライブ前夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Mana Nagase Tribute Live on the eve of the concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ\n通しで何度歌っても完璧な出来ですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew.\nNo matter how many times I sing through it‚ the performance is perfect!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8883145332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。よし、最後の練習はこれくらいにしておこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Alright‚ let's call it the final practice for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7549811999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　私はまだ歌えますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? I can still sing more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8549811999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様のトリビュートライブに出演するのですから\nいくら練習しても足りないくらいですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going to perform at Mana-sama's tribute live‚ after all.\nNo matter how much I practice‚ it's not enough!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "前日に無理は禁物だぞ？　俺の目から見ても\n十分に仕上がっているから、安心して休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouldn't overdo it the day before. From my point of view‚\nyou're already well-prepared‚ so rest assured and take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7883145332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "むぅ……{user}さんがそこまで\n言うなら仕方ありませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… If {user}-san says that much‚\nI suppose it can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "今日はここまでにしておきますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll stop here for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9549811999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いつも頑張ってるけど、今回は特に気合いが入ってるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're always working hard‚ but you seem particularly driven this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}